cat << EOF
A flexible and highly robust polygon set operations library for use with C applications, as referenced in the comp.graphics.algorithms FAQ and the UIUC Computational Geometry Pages. The gpc library is estimated to have thousands of users worldwide, and is subject to several hundred downloads each month.

This software is free for non-commercial use. Anyone wishing to use the gpc library in support of a commercial product please email gpc@cs.man.ac.uk.

Difference
EOF
